# Env (see `.env.example`)

- `GHL_INBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL` вАФ webhook receives `buildGhlPayload()` JSON from `POST /api/submit-lead`.
- `GHL_PIPELINE_ID` вАФ `pit-вА¶` вЖТ payload key `ghlPipelineId`.
- `GHL_LOCATION_ID` вЖТ payload key `ghlLocationId`.
- `GHL_PRIVATE_INTEGRATION_TOKEN` вАФ optional REST API only; never client-side.

Align `api/submit-lead.ts` with `lib/leadApi.ts` when changing payload fields.

# Deploy

Vercel: set env vars on the project; build `pnpm run build` from this directory.
